node.text:
Registered blind at birth, Caroline Casey was brought up as a sighted child. She believed she could see! But what she couldn't see was what was blocking her from reaching her true potential... Something far more powerful than her sight.

#carolinecasey #youarenotyourlabels #lifelesson #reachyourtruepotential #mindsetiseverything #attitude #attitudeiseverything #reachforthestars #goalcastvideos #goalcast #believeinyourself #empoweringwomen

node.title: Caroline Casey- Labels are for packages not people

node.text:
Former Heavyweight boxing champion Mike Tyson was known as the "Baddest Man On Earth". But his confidence and mission to destroy anyone in the ring couldn't hide the fact that he was spiralling out of control. In this video, Mike opens up about his childhood, family tragedy and the truth behind what it really means to be a winner in life.

#miketyson #goalcast #nevergiveup #personalgrowth #boxing #selfjourney #dailymotivation #fighter #motivationalvideos #powerfulmessage #motivated #strongmindset

node.title: Mike Tyson - The Baddest Man On The Planet Destroyed By Shameful Truth

node.text:
Often the most important conversations are the most difficult to have, but one difficult conversation can save you a lot of grief in the long run.
Taking the step to express yourself clearly can often serve as an act of stress-relief and help overall wellbeing. 
It's never an easy task to do, but there are ways to make the process smoother. 
Take a look at our tips below and share your experiences in the comments. 👇

#personalgrowth #growthmindset #personaldevelopment #selfdevelopment #selfcare #wellnesswednesday #anxietytips #mindfulness #entrepreneurlife #careerdevelopment #selfdevelopmentjourney

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Goalcast on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'HOW TO HAVE A DIFFICULT CONVERSATION Goalcast'.

Photo by Goalcast on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'STOP AVOIDING IT Avoiding difficult conversations ensures comfort however confronting them will invite growth into your life. Decide which you value more. Goalcast'.

Photo by Goalcast on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DEFINE KEY TERMS Define key terms you want to discuss. If your partner isn t texting you enough what does 'enough' mean to you? Can you define it? Often our conflicts are fuelled by miscommunication more than anything else. Goalcast'.

Photo by Goalcast on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'REPLACE JUDGEMENT WITH CURIOSITY Curiosity can turn an argument into a conversation. Don't force your point and instead replace rebuttals with softer questions suc as want to fully understand, could you explain that to me a bit more?' Goalcast'.

Photo by Goalcast on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'ALLOW ROOM FOR SILENCE Take time to process your thoughts before you speak. Make space for silence and it'll give you and the other person the chance to process and repond more efficiently. Goalcast'.

Photo by Goalcast on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'KNOW WHEN TO CHECK OUT If the person you're talking to is not listening or making you feel small, calmly walk away. A simple comment such as 'I'm not feeling heard right now' or 'let's revisit this another time, should suffice. Goalcast'.

Registered blind at birth, Caroline Casey was brought up as a sighted child. She believed she could see! But what she couldn't see was what was blocking her from reaching her true potential... Something far more powerful than her sight.

#carolinecasey #youarenotyourlabels #lifelesson #reachyourtruepotential #mindsetiseverything #attitude #attitudeiseverything #reachforthestars #goalcastvideos #goalcast #believeinyourself #empoweringwomen

Former Heavyweight boxing champion Mike Tyson was known as the "Baddest Man On Earth". But his confidence and mission to destroy anyone in the ring couldn't hide the fact that he was spiralling out of control. In this video, Mike opens up about his childhood, family tragedy and the truth behind what it really means to be a winner in life.

If you have a dream, believe you can achieve it, believe you deserve it and start believing you’re going to fulfil it. 

Make today the day you stop questioning yourself, because all of our dreams have the chance to come true if we have the courage to pursue them. 👊 #mondaymotivation 

Video @anthonyhopkins 

#motivationalquotes #motivacion #anthonyhopkins #mindsetmatters #mindsetiseverything #mindsetcoach #entrepreneurlife #entrepreneurmindsets #bethebestyou #growthmindset #growthjourney

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Goalcast on August 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Goalcast Life Isn't Fair. No matter what life throws your way, no matter how unfair it seems, refuse to play the victim. Refuse to be fuelled by fear, pessimism and negativity. Refuse to quit. Because you are a survivor of the unfairness oflife. You are stronger than you think. And are capable of achieving far more than you believe. ZERO DEAN Lessons learned from the path less traveled'.

node.text:
Success comes from commitment, not convenience. ⁠
If you are currently struggling with something, remind yourself of the strength and courage its taken you to overcome every challenge that brought you to this moment. 
Give yourself credit for how far you've come and it'll ignite the power within to take you much further.
